.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-LEDGER-ADD" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-ledger-add \- add a manual ledger entry
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-ledger-add
.I wallet_name direction amount_sat
.RI [ note ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Inserts a manual ledger entry into the wallet database.
Direction is typically
.B credit
or
.BR debit .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"added","wallet":"<name>","amount_sat":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-ledger-search (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-transaction-log (1)
